Acknowledgement:
Most large brands continually diminish trust with their customers online by ignoring them. When your customers and prospects mention your brand, share your content or endorse you within the public domain, you have got to acknowledge them. A simple thank you or even a like says that you appreciate them and acknowledge their faith in you. Take the time to engage with the people who share your content and support your brand.
